          "fileName": "GM_1.2_part04_Mechanics_of_a_System_of_Particles_angular_momentum_center_of_mass_decomposition_Korean_Translation.md",
          "sourcePath": "Units/GM_01_Survey_of_the_Elementary_Principles/GM_1.2_Mechanics_of_a_System_of_Particles/GM_1.2_part04_Mechanics_of_a_System_of_Particles_angular_momentum_center_of_mass_decomposition_Korean_Translation.md",
