          "sourcePath": "Units/GM_01_Survey_of_the_Elementary_Principles/GM_1.6_Simple_Applications_of_the_Lagrangian_Formulation/GM_1.6_part02_Simple_Applications_of_the_Lagrangian_Formulation_cartesian_and_plane_polar_coordinates_KR_TTS.md",
