          "sourcePath": "Units/GM_01_Survey_of_the_Elementary_Principles/GM_1.6_Simple_Applications_of_the_Lagrangian_Formulation/GM_1.6_part03_Simple_Applications_of_the_Lagrangian_Formulation_atwoods_machine_and_rotating_wire_Korean_Translation.md",
